title: How To Install a K&N Air Intake on a 2011-2014 Ford F-150 3.5L Ecoboost
description:
See how easy it is to install a K&N air intake on your 2011 to 2014 Ford F-150 3.5L Ecoboost.

K&N 57-2583 performance air intake system is easy to install and guaranteed to increase horsepower in 2011 to 2014 Ford F-150 with a 3.5L ecoboost engine. When dyno tested, this air intake created an estimated gain of 11 horsepower at 4318 RPM.

This air intake includes an oversized washable & reusable air filter with a chrome top that can go up to 100,000 miles between servicing. K&N air intake 57-2583 also includes a rotomolded polyethylene air intake tube with a large heat shield designed to increase air flow and isolate intake air from engine heat.
